elect" id="btn-10" onclick="selectProduct('Pink Tulip Inspired - ₱300', 'btn-10')">Select 💖</button> </div> </div> </div> <!-- 11 --> <div class="card"> <div class="card-img-wrap" onclick="openModal('IMG11.jpg')"> <img src="IMG11.jpg" alt="Pink Charm" onerror="this.src='https://placehold.co/400x300/ffd6e7/ff6b9d?text=Photo+Coming+Soon'"> <div class="zoom-hint">🔍</div> <span class="card-badge">💗 Cheerful</span> </div> <div class="card-body"> <h3>Pink Charm</h3> <p class="card-desc">A lovely mix of soft pink blooms with a cheerful vibe.</p> <div class="card-footer"> <span class="price">₱280</span> <button class="btn-select" id="btn-11" onclick="selectProduct('Pink Charm - ₱280', 'btn-11')">Select 💖</button> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <!-- ── WHY US ─────────────────────────────────────────── --> <section id="why"> <p class="section-label">Why Choose Us</p> <h2 class="section-title">Made With Love, Every Single Time 💕</h2> <p class="section-sub">Every detail matters to us. Here's what makes every bouquet from us truly special.</p> <div class="features-grid"> <div class="feature-card"> <div class="feature-icon">🌸</div> <h4>100% Handmade</h4> <p>Every bouquet is crafted by hand with care, time, and love — no machines, just heart and dedication.</p> </div> <div class="feature-card"> <div class="feature-icon">💎</div> <h4>Lasts Forever</h4> <p>Unlike real flowers, fuzzy wire bouquets never wilt or fade. A truly memorable gift they'll keep for years.</p> </div> <div class="feature-card"> <div class="feature-icon">🎨</div> <h4>Full Customization</h4> <p>Choose your own colors, designs, and sizes depending on your preference and budget. Your dream bouquet, made real.</p> </div> <div class="feature-card"> <div class="feature-icon">🎁</div> <h4>Perfect for Any Occasion</h4> <p>Birthdays, anniversaries, graduations, Valentine's — a handmade bouquet is always the most thoughtful gift.</p> </div> <div class="feature-card"> <div class="feature-icon">🚛</div> <h4>Nationwide 